Package com.rnb.searsapi.product.pojo.in

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractProductSearchCriteria
    Base Product search Input Criteria.
    CategorySearchCriteria
    To fetch products from an nth-level category, such as to retrieve all of the products in the Refrigerators second-level category under the Appliances top-level category.
    KeywordSearchCriteria
    Keyword search input Criteria - To fetch products based on keyword search, such as to retrieve all of the products with the keyword “cribs”.
    SubCategoriesSearchCriteria
    To fetch category-related information from top-level and nth-level categories, such as the list of second-level categories under the Appliances top-level category, or a range of prices of products in the Refrigerators second-level category under the Appliances top-level category.
    TopSellersSearchCriteria
    The TopSellers Search Criteria data wrapper.

    ProductSearchSortBy
    Product Search Sort criteria enum
